<div id="div_Update-view" class="blurPanel">
    <legend class="legend-title">  <i class="fas fa-clock-o" style="cursor:default;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</i><span style="cursor:default;">{{ 'Dernière vérification : ' }}</span><span class="label label-info" id="span_lastUpdateCheck" style="margin-bottom: 10px;font-size:1em;cursor:default;"></span>
        <input class="form-control" placeholder="{{ 'Rechercher...' }}" id="in_searchPlugin"/>
    </legend>

    <legend class="legend-title"><i class="fas fa-puzzle-piece">&nbsp;&nbsp;</i>{{ 'Plugins' }}</legend>
    <div class="row">
        <div id="listPlugin"></div>
    </div>

    <legend class="legend-title"><i class="fas fa-cubes">&nbsp;&nbsp;</i>{{ 'Autres' }}</legend>
    <div class="row">
        <div id="listOther"></div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="fab" style="z-index:999">
    <span class="fab-action-button"><i class="fab-action-button__icon fas fa-bars"></i></span>
    <ul class="fab-buttons">
        <li class="fab-buttons__item"><a class="fab-buttons__link bg-light-blue-active" id="bt_checkAllUpdate" title="" data-tooltip="{{ 'Vérifier les mises à jour' }}"><i class="fas fa-refresh"></i></a></li>
        <li class="fab-buttons__item"><a class="fab-buttons__link bg-light-blue-active" id="bt_updateNextDom" title="" data-tooltip="{{ 'Mettre à jour' }}"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></a></li>
        <li class="fab-buttons__item"><a class="fab-buttons__link bg-orange" id="bt_doUpdate" title="" data-tooltip="{{ 'Tout mettre à jour' }}"><i class="fas fa-download"></i></a></li>
        <li class="fab-buttons__item"><a class="fab-buttons__link bg-red-active" href="index.php?v=d&p=administration" title="" data-tooltip="{{ 'Retour' }}"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></a></li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div id="md_updateInfo">
    <pre id="pre_updateInfo"></pre>
</div>
<div id="md_specifyUpdate">
    <div class="alert alert-danger">{{ 'Avant toute mise à jour, merci de consulter la note de version du core de NextDom' }} <a target="_blank" href="https://nextdom.github.io/core/fr_FR/noteVersion">{{ 'ici' }}</a></div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-xs-6 control-label label-sticker-big">{{ 'Pré-update (mettre à jour le script d\'update avant)' }}</label>
            <div class="col-xs-4">
                <input type="checkbox" class="updateOption" data-l1key="preUpdate"/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-xs-6 control-label label-sticker-big">{{ 'Sauvegarder avant' }}</label>
            <div class="col-xs-4">
                <input type="checkbox" class="updateOption" data-l1key="backup::before" checked/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-xs-6 control-label label-sticker-big">{{ 'Mettre à jour les plugins' }}</label>
            <div class="col-xs-4">
                <input type="checkbox" class="updateOption" data-l1key="plugins" checked/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-xs-6 control-label label-sticker-big">{{ 'Mettre à jour le core' }}</label>
            <div class="col-xs-4">
                <input type="checkbox" class="updateOption" data-l1key="core" checked/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-xs-6 control-label ">{{ 'Mode forcé' }}</label>
            <div class="col-xs-4">
                <input type="checkbox" class="updateOption" data-l1key="force"/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="alert alert-danger">{{ 'L\'option suivante n\'est à modifier que sur demande du support sinon il faut ABSOLUMENT qu\'elle soit sur "Aucune"' }}</div>
        <div class="form-group has-error">
            <label class="col-xs-6 control-label ">{{ 'Mise à jour à réappliquer' }}</label>
            <div class="col-xs-5">
                <select id="sel_updateVersion" class="form-control updateOption" data-l1key="update::reapply">
                    <option value="">{{ 'Aucune' }}</option>
                    {% for update in updatesList %}
                        <option value="{{ update }}">{{ update }}</option>
                    {% endfor %}
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
